          <avActivityHighlights>New snow and wind slabs in the early morning. The new snow represents the main danger.</avActivityHighlights>
          <avActivityComment>As a consequence of new snow and a sometimes storm force wind, sometimes avalanche prone wind slabs formed in the course of the day in all aspects. In particular on very steep slopes individual small and medium sized avalanches are possible as the snowfall becomes more intense.</avActivityComment>
